<% content_for :title, @mtitle %>
<% content_for :description, @mdescription %>

<div class="container-fluid px-0">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-light py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-4">Property Lawyers in Spain: Trusted Experts for UK, Irish & European Clients</h1>
            
            <p class="lead mb-4">
              Buying or selling a home in Spain should be exciting — not stressful. At Roper Lawyers, we provide clear, trusted legal advice for UK, Irish, and European clients so you can enjoy your Spanish property with complete peace of mind.
            </p>
            
            <p class="mb-4">
              With <strong>14+ years of experience</strong>, <strong>over 1,080 successful conveyancing cases</strong>, and a <strong>5.0 star Google reputation</strong>, we've helped hundreds of expats secure their dream homes in Spain and the Canary Islands.
            </p>
            
            <!-- CTA Button -->
            <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center gap-2">
              <a href="/free-consultation" class="btn rounded-pill hero-primary-btn" 
                 style="background-color: #b39c84; border: none; color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; font-size: 1.125rem; text-decoration: none; min-height: 48px; transition: background-color 0.2s ease;">
                <span style="font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.8px;">Book Free Consultation</span>
              </a>
              <small class="text-muted d-flex align-items-center">
                <%= image_tag("Olivier-Roper-Solicitor-Roper-Lawyers-head.jpg", 
                    alt: "Olivier Roper", 
                    class: "rounded-circle me-2",
                    style: "width: 24px; height: 24px; object-fit: cover;") %>
                Speak directly to Olivier Roper
              </small>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- From Real Estate Roots to Property Law Specialists -->
  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <h2 class="h3 mb-4">From Real Estate Roots to Property Law Specialists</h2>
          
          <p class="mb-3">
            Our story began in 2015, but our family roots in Spanish real estate go back to 1983. Founder Olivier Roper initially trained as an API (Agente de la Propiedad Inmobiliaria) — Spain's official real estate qualification.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-3">
            While studying, he discovered his passion for the legal side of property transactions and went on to complete a law degree at University of Barcelona and a Master's in Madrid.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-4">
            After training at a top law firm, Olivier founded Roper Lawyers, focusing exclusively on property law for foreign buyers and sellers. Today, we are a boutique team that combines deep legal knowledge with practical real estate insight — a unique advantage for our clients.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solving the Language Barrier for Expats -->
  <section class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <h2 class="h3 mb-4">Solving the Language Barrier for Expats</h2>
          
          <p class="mb-3">
            One of the biggest challenges for British and Irish clients in Spain is the language gap. Misunderstandings between lawyers, agents, and buyers can lead to stress and costly mistakes.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-4">
            At Roper Lawyers, we are native bilingual (English & Spanish) and explain every contract, fee, and legal step in plain English. You'll always know exactly what you're signing and why.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Modern, Efficient, and Personal -->
  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <h2 class="h3 mb-4">Modern, Efficient, and Personal</h2>
          
          <p class="mb-3">
            At Roper Lawyers, we believe clients deserve the best of both worlds:
          </p>
          
          <ul class="mb-4">
            <li class="mb-2">The convenience of modern online service when speed and flexibility matter.</li>
            <li class="mb-2">The personal reassurance of face-to-face meetings when you prefer to sit down with your lawyer.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <p class="mb-3">
            We've embraced technology to make property transactions easier for expats abroad. From secure digital signatures to video calls and document sharing, we can now handle most of the process online — saving you flights, delays, and stress.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-3">
            But we also know many of our clients want the comfort of a real office and a trusted lawyer across the table. That's why our doors are always open. Whether you'd like to meet us in person in the Canary Islands or manage everything from your home country, we adapt to your preference.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-4 fw-bold">
            At Roper Lawyers, you never have to choose between modern efficiency and personal service. You get both.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

